{"tid":119243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國旅行團40人在巴黎遇劫　多名團員被毆打","createTime":"2017-02-13T15:04:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-14T11:29:31.000Z","uid":53705,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5dcb7d468fdd0a0029fb46ffb6e54043e29e9e07","tid":119243,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T15:04:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170213/865919.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20170213%2F865919.htm&d=Wvd4d0Ghp%2Fc8oQdY%2BKiOSZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=50a7a296\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.ettoday.net/news/20170213/865919.htm</a><br />\n一個約有40名團員的韓國旅行團日前在法國巴黎遇劫。多名非洲裔劫匪登上他們乘坐的旅遊巴，劫走一批財物，多名旅客還被毆打<br />\n<br />\n韓國旅行團遊覽完艾菲爾鐵塔後，在乘坐旅遊巴士返回飯店途中被4至5名名黑人攔下遊旅巴士。<br />\n<br />\n他們強行登上後，手持碎玻璃瓶等利器威脅乘客，當時巴士上還有孩子。事發10分鐘期間頓時成了地獄。劫匪人喊：「把錢拿出來」，並毆打乘客的頭部。他們搶走旅客的護照、「歐洲之星」高鐵車票和現金，之後揚長而去。 韓國駐法國大使館已要求當地警方徹查此一事件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n韓國人打女人唔係好勁既咩?? 做乜唔打柒果幾個賊"},{"pid":"1057a650c4216e965335605f292943cd997e9524","tid":119243,"uid":57962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T15:04:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4d2ed3ab04992a8f2a22a4c978bcb68c074e1c36","tid":119243,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T15:18:17.000Z","msg":"當過兵既惡爸，仲要人數多過賊"},{"pid":"424cc12b74c93bc66ea62d8f0f28156ac04e2f61","tid":119243,"uid":32473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T15:19:54.000Z","msg":"南泡狗照計應該冇咁易屈服嫁喎話晒當個兵"},{"pid":"413079943cdd6a0776b96d79645e838c1d10570a","tid":119243,"uid":29609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T15:21:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4c286c2efb807c37548502469f83e5